    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age both inside and out. The exterior has some noticeable clear coat peeling and several small dings, while the interior shows significant wear on the driver's seat and some fading on the dashboard. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but it may require some upcoming maintenance like new tires or brake pads soon. It is a solid choice for someone looking for a functional vehicle who doesn't mind some cosmetic imperfections and minor mechanical upkeep.",
