      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in this fantastic find! This vehicle is in good condition, offering a reliable and smooth driving experience that you're going to love. It has been well-maintained and looks great, showing only the typical minor wear you'd expect from a car that's been enjoyed. It's a solid, dependable choice that's ready for its next adventure!",
