    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This expertly maintained vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver. Characterized by its robust mechanical history and a well-preserved aesthetic, this specimen has undergone a comprehensive professional assessment to ensure it meets our exacting standards for performance and reliability. It offers a sophisticated driving experience and remains in commendable condition, ready for immediate delivery. We invite serious inquiries to experience the superior engineering and lasting value of this exceptional automotive offering.",
      "price": 36500.0,
